{"tid":591942,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"好消息》中證監傳完成新經濟公司回歸A股方案","createTime":"2018-03-14T01:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T01:27:27.000Z","uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5dfbc9dec6ff0ce84d927c11566f268e5032132c","tid":591942,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:09:00.000Z","msg":"中證監傳完成新經濟公司回歸A股方案<br />\n<br />\n【中國】 信報財經新聞 15小時前<br />\n0<br />\n【信報財經新聞】中國證監會據報已完成有關新經濟公司回歸A股的改革方案。<br />\n<br />\n內地《第一財經》報道，中證監有關A股對接新經濟的改革方案已形成，正在報批程序當中。滬、深交易所也在中證監指導下積極準備，對於海外上市公司以CDR(中國預託證券)形式回歸A股達成共識。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，目前，針對新經濟企業的投資者保護工作也已經提前研究。<br />\n<br />\n《上海證券報》上周引述全國人大代表、深交所總經理王建軍表示，交易所對CDR已經研究很長時間，今年來看推出CDR的條件已比較成熟。<br />\n<br />\n同股不同權有對手<br />\n有實力怕咩爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58836c562900b8d93bcf81a215003af01c7b8a5","tid":591942,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:11:01.000Z","msg":"開始傳一堆海外股票要回歸<br />\n<br />\n全部人無得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa8e1d76c75cbce28382ee6fdab9c699fbe55a3","tid":591942,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c58836c562900b8d93bcf81a215003af01c7b8a5","tid":591942,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:11:01.000Z","msg":"開始傳一堆海外股票要回歸<br />\n<br />\n全部人無得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:14:45.000Z","msg":"咩牙<br />\n會黎香港上架<br />\n有著數一定益香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098cad3c76994d62dc1905c33e13a31015d2c5b3","tid":591942,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3183214815d082ccb723bda7f64c23f7e7efbd7c","tid":591942,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:24:43.000Z","msg":"Y